    {
        "content": "<p>closest is probably <a href=\"https://leanprover-community.github.io/mathlib4_docs/Mathlib/FieldTheory/PurelyInseparable.html#IntermediateField.adjoin_eq_adjoin_pow_expChar_pow_of_isSeparable\">IntermediateField.adjoin_eq_adjoin_pow_expChar_pow_of_isSeparable</a>; IIRC this predates the extraction of <a href=\"https://leanprover-community.github.io/mathlib4_docs/Mathlib/FieldTheory/Separable.html#IsSeparable\">IsSeparable</a> (<a href=\"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/pull/14232\">#14232</a>), so it's stated as separability of an extension, not an element, but you can use <a href=\"https://leanprover-community.github.io/mathlib4_docs/Mathlib/FieldTheory/SeparableClosure.html#IntermediateField.isSeparable_adjoin_iff_isSeparable\">IntermediateField.isSeparable_adjoin_iff_isSeparable</a>.<br>\ncc <span class=\"user-mention\" data-user-id=\"366779\">@Jz Pan</span></p>",
        "id": 496600915,
        "sender_full_name": "Junyan Xu",
        "timestamp": 1738171685
    },
    {
